125
00:09:37,876 --> 00:09:39,670
- No, paso.
- Vamos, Jasper.

126
00:09:39,753 --> 00:09:42,214
- No pienso contártelo.
- Cuéntalo.

127
00:09:42,297 --> 00:09:45,926
Vale. El Proyecto Humano
da una gran cena...

128
00:09:46,009 --> 00:09:48,554
